Package: Isopair
Type: Package
Title: Isoform Pair Structural Analysis
Version: 0.99.2
Authors@R: person("Pete", "Castaldi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "pcastaldi@bwh.harvard.edu",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7557-338X"))
Description: Detects, characterizes, and compares structural differences
    between isoform pairs. Provides a comprehensive event detection engine
    that identifies 12 types of splicing events (alternative TSS/TES,
    alternative 5'/3' splice sites, skipped exons, intron retention, and
    partial intron retention variants), reconstructs reference isoforms from
    comparator structures, and builds splicing choice profiles for
    downstream analysis.
BiocType: Software
URL: https://changit.bwh.harvard.edu/repjc/Isopair
